and integration.

00:22:14.380 --> 00:22:16.020 position:59%
He will bring Marshall into the NAACP.

00:22:16.020 --> 00:22:20.250 position:70%
In the 30s, he argues in front of the Supreme
Court a number of cases that will strike

00:22:20.250 --> 00:22:23.600
down segregation statutes in
law schools and elsewhere kind

00:22:23.600 --> 00:22:26.270
