the man who killed Jim Crow.

00:22:30.270 --> 00:22:44.020 position:64%
Now he unfortunately dies in I think
1949 or 1950 so he never gets to see 1954

00:22:44.020 --> 00:22:49.650 position:72%
in Brown v. Board of Ed but Thurgood Marshall,
who he brought into the NAACP who he trained

00:22:49.650 --> 00:22:57.010 position:61%
